Project Structure
cricket-streaming-app/
│
├── server.js                 # Main Node.js server file
├── package.json              # Project dependencies
│
├── public/                   # Static assets
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── style.css         # Main stylesheet
│   ├── js/
│   │   └── script.js         # Client-side JavaScript
│   └── images/               # Image assets for channels and sliders
│       ├── cricket-slide1.jpg
│       ├── cricket-slide2.jpg
│       ├── cricket-slide3.jpg
│       ├── star-sports.jpg
│       ├── sky-sports.jpg
│       └── ...
│
└── views/                    # EJS templates
    ├── index.ejs             # Home page
    ├── ipl20.ejs             # IPL streaming page
    ├── pslt20.ejs            # PSL streaming page
    ├── live-cricket.ejs      # Live cricket page
    ├── all-channels.ejs      # All channels page
    ├── channel.ejs           # Individual channel page
    └── partials/             # Reusable template parts
        ├── header.ejs
        └── footer.ejs